Yum! I made this for my annual New Year's Eve party and it was a hit. I doubled the olives (chopped), thyme, and olive oil. I made a goat cheese patty and poured the olive mixture over the cheese and had plenty mixture left to go on the dish around the cheese. Before serving, I placed the whole dish in the microwave for 30 seconds. I will definitely be making this again.

